@startuml
skinparam monochrome true
skinparam packageStyle rectangle
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam sequenceMessageAlign center
autonumber

actor "Backoffice Operator" as BackofficeOperator
participant ":System" as System

activate BackofficeOperator

BackofficeOperator -> System : Requests to list customer's collaborators

activate System
System --> BackofficeOperator : Requests customer identification
deactivate System

BackofficeOperator -> System : Provides customer identification

activate System
System --> System : Check if Backoffice Operator is authorized
System --> System : Validate customer
System --> System : Retrieve customer's active collaborators

alt active collaborators exist
    System --> BackofficeOperator : Display active collaborators list
else no active collaborators exist
    System --> BackofficeOperator : Display empty list message
else customer is invalid or user is unauthorized
    System --> BackofficeOperator : Display error message
end

deactivate System
deactivate BackofficeOperator

@enduml